```

## 样式

在`\themes\next\source\css\_custom\custom.styl`文件中新增

```css
//相册样式
.ImageGrid {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1040px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}

.card {
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: .3s ease-in-out;
  border-radius: 8px;
  background-color: #ddd;
}

.ImageInCard img {
  padding: 0 0 0 0;
  border-radius: 8px;
}
```

